data.description: Cute family home in Columbia County! Close to the fairgrounds and all area shops, schools, dining and hospitals. This 3 Bedroom, 2.5 bath home with covered back patio and fenced in yard is located on a quiet street with sidewalks and street lights. Solid surface floors on the main level. All bedrooms and laundry room are upstairs. The kitchen is well appointed with plenty of cabinet and granite counter space as well as a separate pantry. The owners suite and bath is over sized for comfort! Don't forget the community pool and clubhouse also! Don't miss this one! Call today for your private showing!
